---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import { url } from '../utils/url';
---

<Layout
  title="About — Jodie Plant Marketing"
  description="One marketer. Full attention. Real results. Senior marketing leadership powered by AI-enhanced workflows — no agency bloat."
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-white py-16 sm:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h1 class="font-headline text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold leading-tight">
          One marketer. Full attention. Real results.
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/70 leading-relaxed">
          I'm Jodie Plant — a senior marketer who builds growth systems for startups and tech companies. No junior team running your account. No layers of account managers. Just experienced strategy and execution, enhanced by AI.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- JODIE'S STORY -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">The Short Version</h2>
        <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-lg text-text leading-relaxed">
          <p>
            I've spent 15+ years in digital marketing — from in-house roles at startups to leading campaigns at agencies. I've managed multi-million dollar ad budgets, built content strategies from scratch, and helped companies go from invisible to top of search.
          </p>
          <p>
            I started Jodie Plant Marketing because I saw the same pattern everywhere: talented companies spending money on marketing that wasn't working, managed by people who didn't understand their product or their audience. Junior teams. Cookie-cutter strategies. No one actually paying attention.
          </p>
          <p>
            I do things differently. You get me — not a team of juniors. Every strategy, every campaign, every piece of content has senior-level thinking behind it. And with AI-enhanced workflows, I can deliver what used to take a full team, at a fraction of the cost.
          </p>
          <p class="text-muted">
            Think of me as your fractional CMO — senior marketing leadership without the $300K salary. Strategy AND execution. Not a consultant who leaves you with a PDF.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE APPROACH -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-light">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">How I Work</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted max-w-2xl">Four steps. Complete transparency. No black boxes.</p>

      <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
        <div class="flex gap-5">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-white text-lg">1</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Understand Your Business</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Deep dive into your product, market, competitors, and what's actually driving (or blocking) growth. No assumptions.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-white text-lg">2</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Build Data-Driven Strategy</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Channel selection, messaging, budget allocation — all grounded in data, not gut feel. You'll see exactly where every dollar goes.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-white text-lg">3</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Execute with AI-Enhanced Workflows</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Research, content, optimization, reporting — all enhanced by AI tools. Faster, sharper, more thorough than traditional methods.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5">
          <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 bg-orange rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center font-mono font-bold text-white text-lg">4</span>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-navy">Measure, Report, Iterate</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-muted">Monthly reporting you can actually understand. Clear KPIs. Honest about what's working and what's not. No vanity metrics.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- THE AI ADVANTAGE -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-navy">The AI Advantage</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-muted">AI doesn't replace good marketing. It makes good marketers faster, sharper, and more thorough.</p>

        <div class="mt-10 space-y-6">
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-1 bg-orange rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy">Research at Scale</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-muted">Competitor analysis, keyword research, and market intelligence that used to take weeks — done in hours.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-1 bg-orange rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy">Content Optimization</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-muted">AI-powered content workflows that ensure every piece is optimized for search, AI citation, and conversion.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-1 bg-orange rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy">Campaign Intelligence</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-muted">Faster testing cycles, smarter budget allocation, real-time optimization across platforms.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-4">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-1 bg-orange rounded-full"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy">Reporting &amp; Insights</h3>
              <p class="mt-1 text-muted">Automated reporting that surfaces what matters. Less time in spreadsheets, more time on strategy.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-text font-medium">
          The bottom line: AI augments human strategy — it doesn't replace it. You still get experienced judgment and creative thinking. You just get more of it, faster.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-16 sm:py-20 bg-navy text-white">
    <div class="max-w-container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold">Let's talk about your marketing</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-white/70 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        Whether you need a full strategy or just want a fresh perspective — I'm here.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
        <a href={url('/contact')} class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-orange text-white font-bold text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-orange/90 transition-colors min-h-[44px]">
          Get Your Free Visibility Snapshot
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:jodie@jodieplant.com" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border border-white/20 text-white font-medium text-lg rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 transition-colors min-h-[44px]">
          Email Me Directly
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
